                     <interp inst="t18320705-160-off843" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18320705-160-cd844" type="crimeDate">9th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320705-160-off843 t18320705-160-cd844"></join>, 11 shirts, value 3l., and 1 handkerchief, value 4s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18320705-160-victim1358" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Spiller
                  <interp inst="t18320705-160-victim1358" type="surname" value="Spiller"></interp>
